dct_title_s: Map showing the Freeholders location of the bulkhead line in front of the property of the National Stock Yard Co., Weehawken, N.J. II
dct_description_sm: Map covers area from the Weehawken Ferry Co. property to the property of Patrick Dickey in Weehawken, N.J. Map shows the Freeholders bulkhead line as well as the proposed turnpike.
